name: study iii
description:
oil on canvas

a driving force that articulates desiring movements sublimated in matter and visual with their crossings, which makes the image harbor in itself a drive heritage that is pure information of the movement of the world through the
libidinal thrust.


this series is an attempt to treat the metamorphic manifestations of plastic matter are approached as transformations of it and its symptoms, transformations which record and generate new visual information...
